reviewText: A co-worker told me about this show.  I watched one episode and I was hooked.  Has a great story line and keeps you interested.  Kurt Sutter is a genius.
Bought it for a gift. My husband loves it!
There are portions of a scenes missing
I thought that its was terrible in every measurable way.  No fault of Amazon
My fiance and I love Sons Of Anarchy, he is the one that got me hooked on it
Dvds skipped a few times. But otherwise happy on the deal I got
Parts with no sound & parts with no pic or pic frozen.  Would not buy this at all.  Big waste of good money!!
